def multi_add(*args):
    return sum(args)
funcs = Functions()
funcs['MultiAdd'] = Function('Sum of all arguments', multi_add)
request = json.dumps({'body': {'function': 'MultiAdd', 'data': {'_arg1':
    list(range(1, 10)), '_arg2': list(range(1, 10))}}})
x = funcs.render_evaluate(request, do_print=False)
assert x == '[2, 4, 6, 8, 10, 12, 14, 16, 18]'
